title: Ouija Origin Of Evil Horror 2016 Eng Fre Ita Spa
description:
Plot
In 1967 Los Angeles, widowed mother Alice Zander (Elizabeth Reaser) 
unwittingly invites authentic evil into her home by adding a new stunt to 
bolster her séance scam business. When the merciless spirit overtakes her 
youngest daughter Doris (Lulu Wilson), the small family must confront 
unthinkable fears to save her and send her possessor back to the other side
